<br>
When fighting through dungeons or doing other aspects, there will also be a main assist.  The main assist can be different from the MT, becuase the job is very different.  The main assist will choose which target the raid is going to attack, while enchanters mez the other mobs, or they are tank mezzed by other warriors.<br>
<br>
That leads us into the next job that warriors will serve, the tank mez.  In many high level zones, there are unmezzable mobs, so when you get muiltiples, you have warriors asigned to tank mez those mobs until the MA targets that mob and the raid kills it.<br>
<br>
Many raids will also have a secondary assist, incase the MA dies.<br>
<br>
One other roll that warriors have to fill, is against rampaging mobs.  Rampaging mobs can hit as many as 4 different people at a time, so you will have dedicated ramapage tanks that take the extra damage from the mob.  These tanks will sometimes need a CH rotation to keep them alive, other times, just a dedicated cleric.<br>
<br>
<br>
